word_mean_info__list.difference: 书面用词，指撤销立法机关通过的协议、法案或法律等。
用法广泛，多指取消债务、合同、证书、比赛、旅行、计划或约会等。
正式用词，指彻底废除某种制度、规章或习俗。

bilingual.target: 他们决定取消这个项目。

bilingual.source: We have to cancel our travel plans.
bilingual.target: 我们不得不取消旅行计划。

bilingual.source: I need to cancel my dentist appointment.
bilingual.target: 我需要取消我的牙医预约。

bilingual.source: We were forced to cancel our travel plans.
bilingual.target: 我们被迫取消了旅行计划。

bilingual.source: I decided to cancel my magazine subscription.
bilingual.target: 我决定取消我的杂志订阅。

bilingual.source: We will cancel the game only if it rains.
bilingual.target: 除非下雨，我们才会取消比赛。

bilingual.source: She unilaterally decided to cancel the meeting.
bilingual.target: 她单方面地决定取消会议。

list.abstract: CANCEL是一个英文单词，翻译为取消、撤销；约去、删除。

yingyinNormal.en: You didn't cancel the fabric order from Taiwan?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你没有取消台湾的布料订单？

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, sir. I thought you were gonna cancel my afternoon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是，先生。我不是说要取消下午的事吗。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, thank you, but maybe I should cancel. It's too late to cancel. You're going.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢，但或许我该取消面试。现在取消太晚了，你一定要去。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, well, I'm gonna have to call and cancel the order.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我要去打电话取消订单。

yingyinNormal.en: They can't cancel our play on Christmas Eve. Who does that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们不能取消我们平安夜的戏。谁决定的？

yingyinNormal.en: I don't mind. I'll cancel them. I would never miss my secretary's birthday.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不介意，我可以取消，我不想错过我秘书的生日。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm so sorry, Miranda. If you want me to cancel your evening, I can.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很抱歉，马琳达，如果你想把晚上的活动取消，我去通知。

yingyinNormal.en: Why don't we cancel our dinner reservation and the three of us celebrate Valentine's here?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们何不取消晚餐预订，我们三个一起在家里庆祝情人节？

yingyinNormal.en: You know, it is going to be difficult but I'm going to cancel my plans so I can do this for my bestie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道吗，尽管会很难，但是我要取消我的安排，为了我的好朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: Psyched for date night. See? And now look, she texted right back. "Gotta cancel. Can't leave Dennis."
yingyinNormal.zh: 很期待晚上的约会，看吧？现在看看她的回复，“要取消，不能留下丹尼斯” 。

yingyinNormal.en: No he won't. And that's not even the point. Monica, I made a whole speech about you do not cancel plans with friends.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，他不会的，那根本不是重点，我教训他不该取消朋友之间的计划。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey Joey I have to cancel racket-ball for tonight, that was Marcel's trainer. He's gonna let me have him for a couple of hours.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔伊，我要取消今晚的壁球，马修的训练师会把马修让给我几个小时。

yingyinNormal.en: Let me get this straight. I called yesterday to try to cancel my reservation was told it's not refundable. Then we drove six hours all the way up here and now you're telling me we don't have a reservation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我搞清楚，我有打过电话来试着要取消我的预约，你们告诉我不能取消，然后我们开了六小时的车到这里，现在你又说我们没有订房？

yingyinNormal.en: We're going now. Aunt Rosamund doesn't want to cancel dinner tonight. She thinks we should all be together on a day like today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要走了，罗斯孟德姑妈不想取消今晚的晚宴，她觉得这样的日子我们该待在一起。

yingyinNormal.en: He begged the TNT network to cancel Babylon 5.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他求过TNT电视网砍掉《巴比伦五号》。

yingyinNormal.en: Three times. He begged the Fox network not to cancel Firefly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 求过三次。他求过福克斯电视网不要砍掉《萤火虫》。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, then we'll cancel the announcement. I'll find someone else to be my running mate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，那就不公布了，我另找个竞选伙伴好了。

yingyinNormal.en: No. They can't just cancel a show like Alphas. You know? They have to help the viewers let go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一定要，他们怎么能砍了这样的剧呢？他们应该帮助观众放手才对啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh what? Is she gonna cancel on me again? How can she do this? Doesn't she know it's our anniversary?
yingyinNormal.zh: 她又要爽约了？她怎么可以这样？我们的周年纪念日怎么办？

yingyinNormal.en: There is no season three. They canceled that show. Well, they can't cancel it. It ended on a cliffhanger. They did.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不会有第三季，这剧被砍了。他们不能砍这个剧，季末留了大悬念呢。他们就是砍了。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

sense_info_list.zh: 取消; 撤销; 废除

examination_example.sentence: Think about the times you felt tricked by a membership that had a seamless sign-up process but was later difficult to <highlight>cancel</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 想想你被一个拥有无缝注册过程但后来很难取消的会员资格所欺骗的时候。

examination_example.sentence: Suppose you have to <highlight>cancel</highlight> your travel plan and will not be able to visit Professor Smith.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 假设你不得不取消旅行计划，不能去拜访史密斯教授。

sense_info_list.en: (of a factor or circumstance) neutralize or negate the force or effect of another
delete an equal factor from both sides of an equation or from the numerator and denominator of a fraction
mark, pierce, or tear (a ticket, check, or postage stamp) to show that it has been used or invalidated
